00:13:48,370 --> 00:13:49,620
<i>she writes her report.</i>

213
00:13:50,372 --> 00:13:52,672
<i>A closed meeting of doctors listens</i>

214
00:13:52,916 --> 00:13:57,296
<i>as Dr. Fletcher describes Zelig
