215
00:13:58,505 --> 00:14:02,925
<i>Like the lizard that is endowed by nature
with a marvelous protective device</i>

216
00:14:03,093 --> 00:14:07,263
<i>that enables it to change color and
blend in with its immediate surrounding,</i>

217
00:14:08,181 --> 00:14:11,891
<i>Zelig, too, protects himself
by becoming whoever he is around.</i>

218
00:14:12,936 --> 00:14:15,306
<i>The doctors listen,
