315
00:19:55,320 --> 00:19:58,414
NARRATOR: <i>The crowds that lined
the roads to glimpse the human chameleon</i>

316
00:19:58,489 --> 00:20:00,199
<i>tie up traffic for days.</i>

317
00:20:00,450 --> 00:20:03,580
<i>He is a sight to behold
for tourists and children.</i>

318
00:20:04,078 --> 00:20:08,748
