00:20:29,062 --> 00:20:31,232
<i>of Leonard's stunning prowess.</i>

323
00:20:31,314 --> 00:20:36,154
<i>He does not disappoint, changing
appearance over and over upon demand.</i>

324
00:20:36,736 --> 00:20:41,866
